/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

#welcome-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    height: 50%;
    background: rgba(173, 173, 173, 0.8);
    color: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 2s ease, transform 2s ease;
    transform: translateY(100%);
    z-index: 10000;
}

#welcome-overlay h3 {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 5rem;
}

#welcome-overlay p {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    direction: ltr;
}

#welcome-overlay.showWelcome {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
}

#welcome-overlay.hideWelcome {
    animation: shakeAndSlide 2s ease forwards;
}

button#got-it-button {
    padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a3252, #7a3a9d);
    color: var(--blue-light-color);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 10px 10px 40px 40px;
}

button#got-it-button:hover {
    background-color: #ccc;
}

@keyframes shakeAndSlide {
    0% {
        transform: translateY(0) translateX(0);
        opacity: 1;
    }

    20% {
        transform: translateY(10px) translateX(-10px);
    }

    40% {
        transform: translateY(20px) translateX(10px);
    }

    60% {
        transform: translateY(30px) translateX(-10px);
    }

    80% {
        transform: translateY(40px) translateX(10px);
    }

    100% {
        transform: translateY(100%) translateX(0);
        opacity: 0;
    }
}

/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/
/*═════════════════════╣ End of Welcoming ╠═════════════════════*/
/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/
/*═════════════════════╣ Start of Header ╠═════════════════════*/
/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

.header {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    direction: ltr;
    font-size: 4.2rem;
    height: 210px;
    background: var(--purple-secondary-color);
    animation: header-load var(--header-load-time) ease-in;
}

.header-p {
    animation: names-header var(--names-header-time) ease-out;
}

.header p:nth-child(1) {
    color: var(--blue-light-color);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.header p:nth-child(2) {
    color: var(--blue-light-color);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

#logo-header {
    animation: var(--logo-header-time) ease-out 900ms 1 logo-header;
    animation-fill-mode: backwards;
}

#logo-header img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 192px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
}

#header-nav {
    color: var(--dark-primary-color);
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 70px;
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #ffde5d, #ffd633, #ffd11a);
    width: 100%;
    float: right;
    margin: 0 auto;
    transition: .4s ease-out;
    animation: nav-load var(--nav-load-time) ease-in;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 10000;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 15px 2px var(--yellow-primary-color);
}

@media screen and (max-width:500px) {
    #header-nav {
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px var(--yellow-primary-color);
    }
}

@media screen and (max-width:350px) {
    #header-nav {
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px var(--yellow-primary-color);
    }

    #entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards {
        width: 230px !important;
        height: 350px !important;
    }
}

nav .openMenu .fa-bars {
    font-size: 3rem;
}

nav .mainMenu {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
}

nav .openMenu {
    font-size: 2rem;
    padding: 20px;
    display: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 20%;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

#header-nav ul li {
    position: relative;
    margin: 0 auto;
    transition: .4s ease-out;
    animation-name: nav-link-load;
    animation-duration: var(--nav-link-load-time);
    animation-timing-function: ease-out;
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
    transform: scale(0);
    opacity: 0.6;
}

#header-nav ul li.active {
    opacity: 1;
    text-shadow: -3px 3px 7px #4d4d00;
}

#header-nav ul li:hover {
    opacity: 1;
}

#header-nav ul li:nth-child(odd) {
    animation-name: nav-odd-link-load;
    animation-timing-function: ease-out;
    animation-delay: var(--nav-load-time);
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
    transform: translateY(10000%);
}

#header-nav ul li:nth-child(even) {
    animation-name: nav-even-link-load;
    animation-timing-function: ease-in;
    animation-delay: var(--nav-load-time);
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
    transform: translateY(-1000%);
}

#header-nav ul .icons {
    animation: none;
}

nav .mainMenu li a {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--dark-primary-color);
    padding: 21px;
    display: inline-block;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 2rem;
}

.anchor {
    display: block;
    height: 70px;
    margin-top: -70px;
    visibility: hidden;
}

.fixed {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1;
}

@media (max-width: 850px) {
    .header {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
    }

    #threejs-btn {
        width: 100% !important;
    }
}

nav .mainMenu .closeMenu,
.icons i {
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.fa-linkedin:hover {
    color: rgb(0, 0, 204) !important;
}

.fa-twitter:hover {
    color: rgb(86, 154, 243) !important;
}

.fa-instagram:hover {
    color: rgb(255, 0, 191) !important;
}

.fa-github:hover {
    color: rgb(255, 123, 0) !important;
}

.icons {
    display: none;
}

@media (max-width: 867px) {
    nav .mainMenu {
        min-height: 100vh;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background: var(--purple-primary-color);
        transition: top 1s ease;
        display: none;
    }

    nav .mainMenu .closeMenu {
        display: block;
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        color: #fff;
    }

    nav .openMenu {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--purple-primary-color);
    }

    nav .mainMenu li a:hover {
        background: none;
        color: var(--yellow-primary-color);
    }

    .icons {
        display: inline-flex;
    }

    .icons i {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px;
        color: #fff;
    }

    nav .mainMenu li a {
        color: #fff;
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
        width: 1.25vw !important;
    }
}

@keyframes nav-load {
    0% {
        transform: translateY(-100%);
    }

    100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes names-header {
    0% {
        opacity: 0;
    }

    100% {
        opacity: 1;
    }
}

@keyframes nav-link-load {
    0% {
        transform: scale(0);
    }

    80% {
        transform: scale(1.2);
    }

    100% {
        transform: scale(1);
    }
}

@keyframes nav-odd-link-load {
    0% {
        transform: translateY(10000%);
    }

    90% {
        transform: translateY(-50%);
    }

    100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes nav-even-link-load {
    0% {
        transform: translateY(-1000%);
    }

    90% {
        transform: translateY(50%);
    }

    100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes header-load {
    0% {
        transform: translateY(100%);
    }

    100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes logo-header {
    0% {
        transform: translateY(-1000%);
    }

    100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

