/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

#entrepreneur-quotes {
    background: rgba(168, 198, 222, .2);
    border-radius: 15px 300px;
    padding: 3rem 0;
    margin: 2rem 5rem;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards {
    width: 265px;
    height: 400px;
    position: relative;
    background: #000;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 10%;
    margin: 40px auto;
    transform: translateY(25%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 500ms ease-in, transform 400ms ease-in;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards.appear {
    transform: translateY(0);
    opacity: 1;
    transition: transform 300ms ease-in-out;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards.appear:hover {
    transform: translateX(4px) skew(0.5deg, -0.4deg);
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards::before {
    content: '';
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    position: absolute;
    pointer-events: none;
}

.quotes-test:nth-child(2) .cards,
.quotes-test:nth-child(2) .cards .overlay {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3503ad, #f7308c);
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 7px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, .5);

}

.quotes-test:nth-child(3) .cards,
.quotes-test:nth-child(3) .cards .overlay {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ccff00, #09afff);
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px 7px rgba(0, 0, 0, .8);
}

.quotes-test:nth-child(4) .cards,
.quotes-test:nth-child(4) .cards .overlay {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e91e63, #ffeb3b);
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 7px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, .5);
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards .imgBx {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 10%;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: absolute;
    transform: skew(10px, 10px);
}

.quotes-test h3 {
    padding: 0;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px black;
    color: var(--yellow-primary-color);
    font-family: Cursive;
    text-shadow: 4px 4px 5px #D4AF37;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards .overlay {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    display: flex;
    position: absolute;
    right: 20px;
    bottom: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: .5s;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards .overlay:hover {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    box-shadow: none;
    opacity: .9;
    border-radius: 10%;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards .overlay::before {
    content: 'بخوان';
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    transition-delay: .5s;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards .overlay:hover::before {
    display: none;
    transition-delay: .5s;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards .content {
    padding: 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    color: #fff;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: 0s;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 2;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
}

#entrepreneur-quotes-container .cards .overlay:hover~.content {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
    transition: .2s;
    transition-delay: .5s;
}

.imgBx img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 10%;
}

@media (max-width: 980px) {
    #entrepreneur-quotes {
        border-radius: 15px 150px;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 500px) {
    #entrepreneur-quotes {
        border-radius: 15px 75px;
    }

    #Skills {
        border-radius: 100px 15px;
    }

    .threejs-modal-content__upper h2 {
        font-size: 1.7rem;
    }
}

